<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <meta name="description" content="المشروع غير موجود - Golf House Development">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@300;400;500;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          fontFamily: { tajawal: ['Tajawal', 'sans-serif'] },
          colors: {
            gold: { 50: '#fdf9e7', 100: '#fbf0b5', 200: '#f5e06b', 300: '#e8c820', 400: '#d4af37', 500: '#b8960c', 600: '#957a0a', 700: '#715c08', 800: '#4d3f06', 900: '#2a2103' },
            dark: { 50: '#f5f5f5', 100: '#e0e0e0', 200: '#b0b0b0', 300: '#808080', 400: '#505050', 500: '#303030', 600: '#252525', 700: '#1a1a1a', 800: '#111111', 900: '#0a0a0a' }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body class="font-tajawal bg-dark-900 text-white min-h-screen">
  <!-- Animated golden background -->
  <div class="fixed inset-0 z-0">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-dark-900 via-dark-800 to-dark-900"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 40%, rgba(212,175,55,0.4) 0%, rgba(212,175,55,0.1) 40%, transparent 70%);"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 60%, rgba(184,150,12,0.3) 0%, transparent 50%);"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-screen px-4 py-8">
    <div class="text-center animate-fadeIn w-full max-w-3xl">
      <!-- warning icon -->
      <div class="mb-8">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500/20 to-red-600/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-red-500/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
             <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 leading-relaxed text-white">
        عذراً، يبدو أن المشروع تم حذفه أو تعديله
      </h1>

      <p class="text-dark-200 text-lg mb-12 max-w-md mx-auto">
        المشروع الذي تبحث عنه غير متاح حالياً. يرجى اختيار أحد المشاريع المتاحة أدناه لمتابعة طلبك:
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-right">
        <% if (projects && projects.length > 0) { %>
          <% projects.forEach(function(project) { %>
            <a href="/form/<%= project.slug %>" class="bg-dark-800/80 backdrop-blur border border-gold-400/20 hover:border-gold-400/60 p-5 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-gold-400/10 group flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="font-bold text-lg text-white group-hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors"><%= project.name %></span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-dark-300 group-hover:text-gold-400 transform -rotate-180 transition-all group-hover:-translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
            </a>
          <% }); %>
        <% } else { %>
          <div class="col-span-full text-center text-dark-300 p-8 border border-dark-700/50 rounded-2xl bg-dark-800/50">
            لا توجد مشاريع متاحة حالياً في قاعدة البيانات.
          </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-16">
        <a href="https://golfhousedevelopment.com/" class="text-gold-400 hover:text-gold-300 underline underline-offset-4 decoration-gold-400/30 transition-colors text-lg">
          العودة للموقع الرئيسي
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
